These aren't your typical bulky gaming laptops that sound like jet engines. I tested Lenovo's new Legion Pro series - including a maxed-out $4,500 beast with RTX 5090 - to see if their new "hyper chamber" cooling actually works, or if it's just marketing hype. The results might surprise you, especially when it comes to which model offers the best bang for your buck.
